1. mouse focus
   1. click on input
   2. select item with mouse
   3. focus should be on input

2. open dropdown with arrow down key

3. close dropdown with esc key

4. switch between existing filled items with tab/shift+tab or cursor left/right

5. do not accept item when pressing shift+tab

6. when tabbing into the fbckeditor, do not focus the "x" of the first item but the first one completely

8. make the input field as wide as the whole area
